game.name: At the end zombies win
game.description:
It is time to come forward and load yourself with everything that can help save your life against a horde of deadly souls. Use anything as a weapon to stand strong against the blood-thirsty zombies! The post-apocalyptic universe is invaded by the disgustingly absurd zombies who know nothing but how to take your life. You are only one left in your group. Pick up the weapon in your hand and get ready to show the world that you would not let yourself get eaten easily!
At the end zombies win is an awesome zombie game where you fight against the undead. Believe us, the victory will be yours for sure if you challenge your speed and management ability as well as reflexes. The zombie apocalypse breaks out and there will a very less chance of the survival for any human being in the end. However, being a hero of your group, you have decided to fight for survival and make people of your group feel proud on you. Use a shotgun, a gun or a knife to survive as long as you can!
Play wisely to collect coins and buy new weapons for yourself in this one of the most popular zombie shooter! Try to put your quick reflexes to test and save mankind by defeating the apocalypse! Your survival against the infinite waves of zombies will help you to move towards the more complex level where stronger and powerful creatures are waiting for you. Eliminate all of them to wear the crown of a king of survival! It is our endeavour to serve you with more engaging action packed survival games for boys!
